âœ… Final Tips:
Folder Structure:

bash
Copy code
/frontend
  /pages (HTML files)
  /css
  /js
/backend
  /routes
  /models
  server.js
Use a .env file to store secrets (Mongo URI, JWT secret).

Test each route individually before linking them together.

Use Postman to test API calls before frontend is ready.
